{"type": "article", "id": 22747, "title": "俄罗斯风格的扇子", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122208oRjmbpf7i9IGywEQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是俄罗斯设计师 Yaroslav Misonzhnikov 带来的一套实木日用品，包括梳子、镜子和扇子。这一系列都带有俄罗斯的民间元素，梳子和镜子的把手都是半月形的，让自然的木纹成为一种装饰，非常秀丽。扇子是在实木圆框中使用了蕾丝织面，也是在俄罗斯的传统用法中结合了简约的现代风格。<a href=\"http://misonzhnikov.com/portfolio/projects/katerina.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122205u8hsPmHqTGYODVNi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122205t016p2TjZyNUXcnP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122206BroKdk6mqvGx1JVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122206GAYDI27y6WHqjin8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122207RZXQ6xN1wy0s4JtT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}